<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Hakemuksen liite, esim. tosite, todistus tai lomake."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Attachment"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Bilaga"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Liite"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Hakemukseen liitettävä lisämateriaali, joka täydentää tai todentaa hakemuksen tietoja."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Supplementary material attached to an application that completes or substantiates the application's information."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Attachment"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Bilaga"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Liite"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Attachment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Liitettä tarvitaan joskus hakemuksen liitteeksi; pakollisuus on hakemus- tai etuuskohtaista (kuvataan SHACLissa, ei luokkatasolla)."@fi .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/cpsv#PublicService> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A social security benefit or allowance. General class — use subclasses for instances."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Sosiaaliturvan etuus tai tuki. Yleinen luokka — käytä alaluokkia instansseissa."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Benefit"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Etuus"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Förmån"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Social benefit"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Sosiaalietuus"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Tuki"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Benefit"@en .
