<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Förmån"@sv .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Benefit> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#StandaloneBenefit> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Benefit Component"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Osa suurempaa etuuskokonaisuutta."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Benefit Component"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Etuuden osa"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "etuusosa"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "sub-benefit"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An independent and separately processed part of a benefit that can be granted only if the benefit in which the part belongs is also granted."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Etuuden itsenäinen, erikseen käsiteltävä osa, joka voidaan myöntää vain, jos myös etuus, jonka osa on kyseessä, on myönnetty."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Esimerkiksi opintotuessa etuuden osia ovat opintoraha, asumislisä ja opintolainan valtiontakaus; lesken- ja lapseneläkkeessä osia ovat perus- ja täydennysmäärät."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "For example, the study grant, housing supplement and government guarantee for student loan are parts of the financial aid for students."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Benefit Component"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#BenefitComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Etuuden osa"@fi .
