# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Beslut"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Decision"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Päätös"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An authority's resolution on an application; grants or rejects the requested benefit in full or in part."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Viranomaisen ratkaisu hakemukseen; myöntää tai hylkää haetun etuuden kokonaan tai osittain."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Beslut"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Decision"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Decision> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Päätös"@fi .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalResource> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A work in a legislative corpus. This applies to acts that have been legally enacted (whether or not they are still in force). A legal resource can represent a legal act or any component of a legal act, like an article. Legal resources can be linked together using properties defined in the model."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Lainsäädäntöaineistoon kuuluva teos. Tämä koskee lainvoimaisesti säädettyjä lakeja (riippumatta siitä, ovatko ne vielä voimassa). Oikeudellinen resurssi voi edustaa säädöstä tai mitä tahansa säädöksen osaa, kuten artiklaa. Oikeudelliset resurssit voidaan linkittää toisiinsa mallissa määriteltyjen ominaisuuksien avulla."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Juridisk resurs"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Legal Resource"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Säädös"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Tekstikokonaisuus, joka sisältää julkisen vallan antamia yleisesti noudatettaviksi tarkoitettuja säännöksiä."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Text containing provisions issued by public authorities that are to be observed generally."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://schema.org/Legislation> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Examples of statutes are acts and decrees as well as legal provisions issued by authorities."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Säädöksiä ovat esimerkiksi lait ja asetukset sekä viranomaisten antamat oikeussäännöt."@fi .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalResource> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Lain tai asetuksen osa (luku, pykälä, momentti, kohta yms.).\n          Tämä luokka on tarkoitettu erottamaan kokonaiset lait niiden osista. EU-asetuksissa ym. on myös muu jaottelu kuin Suomessa."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Legal Resource Part"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Osa laista riippumatta siitä, onko kyseessä luku, pykälä vai momentti."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lagdel"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lain osa"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Legal Resource Part"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Lain tai asetuksen osa riippumatta siitä, onko kyseessä luku, pykälä vai momentti"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Kansaneläkelain 23 §"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Lagdel"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Lain osa"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LegalResourcePart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Legal Resource Part"@en .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Elämäntilanteilla tarkoitetaan sellaisia muutosvaiheita, joita kuvaa väliaikaisuus, erityisten palvelujen ja tiedon tarve sekä niihin kohdennetut palvelut.\n        Elämäntilanneluokitus on toteutettu muualla skos-luokituksena. Luokituksen luokat ovat käsitteitä. Luokitus on luonnos. Pohjana on käytetty\n        DVV:n elämäntapahtumaluokitusta, joka perustuu EU-luokitukseen."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Life situations refer to phases of change characterized by temporary nature, the need for special services and information, and services targeted to them."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ElämäntilanneLuokitus"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Klassificering av livssituationer"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Life Situation Classification"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#closeMatch> <http://iri.suomi.fi/model/suomiptv2/LifeEventClassification> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Elämäntilanteilla tarkoitetaan sellaisia muutosvaiheita, joita kuvaa väliaikaisuus, erityisten palvelujen ja tiedon tarve sekä niihin kohdennetut palvelut."@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Life situations refer to phases of change characterized by temporary nature, the need for special services and information, and services targeted to them."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ElämäntilanneLuokitus"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Klassificering av livssituationer"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#LifeSituationClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Life Situation Classification"@en .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/org#Organization> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An actor that is an association of individuals with a common goal and a purposeful structure"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Toimija, joka on henkilöiden muodostama yhteenliittymä ja jolla on yhteinen tavoite ja tarkoituksenmukainen rakenne"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Organisaatio"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Organisation"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Organization"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broadMatch> <http://data.europa.eu/m8g/PublicOrganisation> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#closeMatch> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Organization> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://iri.suomi.fi/model/suomiptv2/Organization> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://schema.org/Organization> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Organisaatio"@fi .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Organisation"@sv .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Organization"@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Organisation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "KELAO-kontekstissa vastaa PTV:n Organization-käsitettä ja \n         schema.org/Organization-käsitettä. Käytetään kuvaamaan kaikkia \n         toimijaorganisaatioita sektorirajat ylittäen (julkinen, yksityinen, \n         kolmas sektori). EU Core Public Organisation on tämän erikoistapaus."@fi .
# 
# https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Service
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Service> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/cpsv#PublicService> .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A social-security-related service, e.g. an application or advisory service."@en .
<https://kela.fi/ontology/kelao#Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Sosiaaliturvaan liittyvä palvelu, esim. hakemus- tai neuvontapalvelu."@fi .
